<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Faultless" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Faultless,</orth> innocent: <cit><quote>look thyself be f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.189" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 1, 189</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>any malice should prevail, that f. may condemn a nobleman,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 24</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a clout steeped in the f. blood of pretty Rutland,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.178" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 178</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>